1
00:00:08,130 --> 00:00:11,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey Mama,
what's for dinner tonight?</font>

2
00:00:11,010 --> 00:00:12,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm, let's see...</font>

3
00:00:14,180 --> 00:00:15,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since Dad won't be home,</font>

4
00:00:15,930 --> 00:00:17,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's get
some yakitori from Torishige?</font>

5
00:00:17,810 --> 00:00:19,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?! Yay!</font>

6
00:00:19,890 --> 00:00:21,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I want...</font>

7
00:00:21,730 --> 00:00:24,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gizzard and cheek, and neck,
and esophagus, and chicken tail!</font>

8
00:00:26,270 --> 00:00:28,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your palate is something else.</font>

9
00:00:28,860 --> 00:00:30,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You take after your father.</font>

10
00:00:30,190 --> 00:00:32,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait!
Also their chicken offal stew!</font>

11
00:00:32,610 --> 00:00:34,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How old are you, really?</font>

12
00:00:55,680 --> 00:00:57,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

13
00:00:57,090 --> 00:00:59,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- A Demon?
- It's a Demon!</font>

14
00:01:09,020 --> 00:01:10,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Boy...</font>

15
00:01:10,570 --> 00:01:12,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My...</font>

16
00:01:12,280 --> 00:01:13,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Boy...</font>

17
00:01:15,200 --> 00:01:18,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Where are you?
- Help!</font>

18
00:01:30,040 --> 00:01:32,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My boy!</font>

19
00:01:39,890 --> 00:01:40,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mama!</font>

20
00:01:40,850 --> 00:01:41,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuki!</font>

21
00:01:44,310 --> 00:01:45,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I found you!</font>

22
00:01:49,610 --> 00:01:50,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mama!</font>

23
00:01:50,690 --> 00:01:52,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuki!</font>

24
00:01:53,530 --> 00:01:55,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mama!</font>

25
00:01:55,570 --> 00:01:59,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My...boy!</font>

26
00:02:00,320 --> 00:02:04,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mine...all mine!</font>

27
00:02:05,910 --> 00:02:08,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuki!</font>

28
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:23,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuki!</font>

29
00:02:38,110 --> 00:02:40,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give him back.
My boy...</font>

30
00:02:40,910 --> 00:02:45,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's enough of you Demons
having your way.</font>

31
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:47,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where is...the boy?</font>

32
00:02:48,330 --> 00:02:51,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where is...the boy?</font>

33
00:02:52,290 --> 00:02:55,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where are you, boy?</font>

34
00:02:55,170 --> 00:02:57,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- All of you...
- Boy?</font>

35
00:02:57,970 --> 00:02:59,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...are going down!</font>

36
00:03:13,020 --> 00:03:14,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This...</font>

37
00:03:15,440 --> 00:03:17,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is the story of how one rooster...</font>

38
00:03:19,200 --> 00:03:22,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...saved humanity.</font>

39
00:05:04,510 --> 00:05:06,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}ONE YEAR AGO</font>

40
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:56,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait!</font>

41
00:05:58,520 --> 00:05:59,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you leaving?!</font>

42
00:06:01,150 --> 00:06:05,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was born to wander.
Peace and quiet doesn't suit me.</font>

43
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:07,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Were you just toying with me?</font>

44
00:06:08,860 --> 00:06:09,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No...</font>

45
00:06:11,490 --> 00:06:13,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just gave in
to my animal instincts</font>

46
00:06:16,960 --> 00:06:19,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}EPISODE ONE:
A ROOSTER AMONG CRANES</font>

47
00:06:41,440 --> 00:06:42,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Delicious!</font>

48
00:06:42,980 --> 00:06:45,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The savory aroma and
the perfect amount of bitterness.</font>

49
00:06:45,940 --> 00:06:48,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing like stink bugs
for breakfast.</font>

50
00:06:49,160 --> 00:06:50,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also...</font>

51
00:06:50,490 --> 00:06:54,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're great for digestion and
promote healthy bowel movements.</font>

52
00:06:57,540 --> 00:06:59,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Delicious and good for your health.</font>

53
00:06:59,620 --> 00:07:02,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Truly two birds with one stone!</font>

54
00:07:15,350 --> 00:07:17,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Oh, a chicken!
- Oh, a chicken!</font>

55
00:07:18,730 --> 00:07:20,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His comb is so cute!</font>

56
00:07:20,390 --> 00:07:21,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you think it's a stray chicken?</font>

57
00:07:21,900 --> 00:07:22,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where did you come from?</font>

58
00:07:22,980 --> 00:07:24,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Probably the zoo?</font>

59
00:07:24,190 --> 00:07:26,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- That would be funny!
- I hate kids.</font>

60
00:07:26,730 --> 00:07:29,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're rude, stubborn and loud.</font>

61
00:07:29,860 --> 00:07:31,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, do you want some?</font>

62
00:07:33,530 --> 00:07:36,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fried chicken!
It's good!</font>

63
00:07:37,450 --> 00:07:39,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is she for real?</font>

64
00:07:43,500 --> 00:07:45,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a cool find!</font>

65
00:07:45,250 --> 00:07:47,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop it,
you're hurting the poor thing!</font>

66
00:07:48,090 --> 00:07:49,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up, you brat!</font>

67
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:52,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Let's go.
- Yeah.</font>

68
00:07:52,340 --> 00:07:54,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa, his comb's so cool.</font>

69
00:07:54,510 --> 00:07:56,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're still brats too!</font>

70
00:07:56,310 --> 00:07:57,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right!</font>

71
00:07:59,520 --> 00:08:00,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What should we do with him?</font>

72
00:08:00,850 --> 00:08:02,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanna eat him.</font>

73
00:08:02,230 --> 00:08:04,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You idiot, what if he's got
some weird disease?</font>

74
00:08:04,810 --> 00:08:05,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right.</font>

75
00:08:05,820 --> 00:08:08,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about we feed him to my cat?</font>

76
00:08:08,860 --> 00:08:10,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, good idea!</font>

77
00:08:11,900 --> 00:08:12,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa!</font>

78
00:08:12,860 --> 00:08:13,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait!</font>

79
00:08:14,280 --> 00:08:15,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, wait!</font>

80
00:08:17,410 --> 00:08:20,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't waste my time,
you little punks!</font>

81
00:08:23,080 --> 00:08:25,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop, dang it!</font>

82
00:08:25,880 --> 00:08:27,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They just won't quit!</font>

83
00:08:35,430 --> 00:08:37,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold it!</font>

84
00:08:50,940 --> 00:08:52,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's going on?</font>

85
00:08:52,400 --> 00:08:54,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That rooster's ours.</font>

86
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:56,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

87
00:09:00,450 --> 00:09:02,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, that's odd...</font>

88
00:09:02,500 --> 00:09:04,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That rooster lives here with me...</font>

89
00:09:04,710 --> 00:09:05,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

90
00:09:05,750 --> 00:09:07,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Cluckers!</font>

91
00:09:07,710 --> 00:09:10,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How many times have I told you
not to leave the yard?!</font>

92
00:09:10,590 --> 00:09:11,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr...Cluckers?!</font>

93
00:09:12,420 --> 00:09:15,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, we'll be more careful
in the future.</font>

94
00:09:19,060 --> 00:09:20,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's get out of here!</font>

95
00:09:24,940 --> 00:09:26,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You saved my feathers, Old Man.</font>

96
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:34,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you think that chicken
really belongs to the old man?</font>

97
00:09:34,700 --> 00:09:36,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You idiot, of course he's lying!!</font>

98
00:09:36,700 --> 00:09:38,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- That old geezer!
- My quota...</font>

99
00:09:38,160 --> 00:09:39,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">-Think he's gonna
-My quota.</font>

100
00:09:39,370 --> 00:09:40,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">gonna eat him all by himself?</font>

101
00:09:40,700 --> 00:09:42,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This month for sure,</font>

102
00:09:42,580 --> 00:09:44,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll definitely...</font>

103
00:09:44,210 --> 00:09:45,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Meet my quota!</font>

104
00:09:45,460 --> 00:09:46,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My quota!</font>

105
00:09:48,380 --> 00:09:49,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Much obliged,
Old Man.</font>

106
00:09:50,460 --> 00:09:53,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I've got things
to take care of.</font>

107
00:09:55,800 --> 00:09:58,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so sorry.
This is all I can give you.</font>

108
00:10:00,260 --> 00:10:02,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Brown rice, corn and shiso leaves?</font>

109
00:10:03,270 --> 00:10:04,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Old man...</font>

110
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:08,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is undeniably a special
and bountiful feast!</font>

111
00:10:10,480 --> 00:10:13,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it good?
I'm glad you like it.</font>

112
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:23,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My wife would always
feed the sparrows</font>

113
00:10:23,330 --> 00:10:25,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that would come and visit as well...</font>

114
00:10:28,370 --> 00:10:29,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looking back...</font>

115
00:10:30,670 --> 00:10:33,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should have retired
from teaching sooner,</font>

116
00:10:33,340 --> 00:10:36,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and spent more time with her.</font>

117
00:10:43,680 --> 00:10:46,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on now, don't fight.</font>

118
00:10:46,680 --> 00:10:48,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't eat too fast, now.</font>

119
00:11:01,320 --> 00:11:03,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry for rambling.</font>

120
00:11:03,950 --> 00:11:07,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For some reason I feel like
I can talk to you about anything.</font>

121
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:10,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I understand, Old Man.</font>

122
00:11:11,630 --> 00:11:14,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should've spent
more time with them as well.</font>

123
00:11:15,630 --> 00:11:16,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Big Brother!</font>

124
00:11:21,220 --> 00:11:22,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Big Brother!</font>

125
00:11:24,510 --> 00:11:25,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Big Brother!</font>

126
00:11:26,390 --> 00:11:29,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Big Brother!!</font>

127
00:11:29,980 --> 00:11:31,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sarah!</font>

128
00:11:32,190 --> 00:11:33,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Big Brother!</font>

129
00:11:38,070 --> 00:11:39,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sarah!!</font>

130
00:11:45,620 --> 00:11:48,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Big Brother!</font>

131
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:52,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sarah!!</font>

132
00:12:07,810 --> 00:12:09,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was that?!</font>

133
00:12:16,940 --> 00:12:19,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Model upgrade!</font>

134
00:12:19,490 --> 00:12:22,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">High-value trade-in!</font>

135
00:12:22,410 --> 00:12:27,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Emergency evacuation alert.
A Demon has appeared</font>

136
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:33,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Evacuate the area immediately.</font>

137
00:12:38,340 --> 00:12:39,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A Demon!</font>

138
00:12:40,130 --> 00:12:46,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This month, I will
meet my quota!</font>

139
00:12:52,270 --> 00:12:54,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Help!
- Help!</font>

140
00:12:54,810 --> 00:12:56,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's those brats from earlier!</font>

141
00:13:00,440 --> 00:13:01,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hiroshi!</font>

142
00:13:02,030 --> 00:13:03,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ow!</font>

143
00:13:06,870 --> 00:13:09,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Quota...</font>

144
00:13:11,540 --> 00:13:12,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry, run!</font>

145
00:13:13,580 --> 00:13:16,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...achieved!</font>

146
00:13:20,380 --> 00:13:21,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Old Man!</font>

147
00:13:38,190 --> 00:13:39,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A recall?</font>

148
00:13:51,490 --> 00:13:53,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now's our chance!
Come on!</font>

149
00:13:54,410 --> 00:13:55,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey you!</font>

150
00:13:56,290 --> 00:13:59,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think you're doing
to those kids and old people?</font>

151
00:14:00,040 --> 00:14:03,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It really makes my crown curl!</font>

152
00:14:28,450 --> 00:14:33,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I achieved my quota!</font>

153
00:14:38,710 --> 00:14:42,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're going down!!!</font>

154
00:14:44,090 --> 00:14:47,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Special edition model!</font>

155
00:14:57,100 --> 00:14:58,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hybrid vehicle!</font>

156
00:14:58,270 --> 00:14:59,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hydrogen engine!</font>

157
00:15:09,820 --> 00:15:11,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My goal...</font>

158
00:15:11,160 --> 00:15:14,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...is to be first
in national rankings!</font>

159
00:15:38,850 --> 00:15:39,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Domestics!</font>

160
00:15:40,020 --> 00:15:41,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Imports!</font>

161
00:15:41,730 --> 00:15:43,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Domestics!</font>

162
00:15:43,730 --> 00:15:44,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Amazing...</font>

163
00:16:06,500 --> 00:16:07,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Finishing move!</font>

164
00:16:13,590 --> 00:16:14,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take this!</font>

165
00:16:16,350 --> 00:16:17,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ko...</font>

166
00:16:18,310 --> 00:16:19,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ke...</font>

167
00:16:19,890 --> 00:16:21,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kok...</font>

168
00:16:22,730 --> 00:16:26,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ko!!!</font>

169
00:16:22,770 --> 00:16:25,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}KOKEKOKKO</font>

170
00:16:49,010 --> 00:16:53,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sales report!</font>

171
00:17:13,450 --> 00:17:15,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What just happened?</font>

172
00:17:15,410 --> 00:17:16,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it possible?</font>

173
00:17:17,580 --> 00:17:20,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It might have been the phenomena
known as resonance.</font>

174
00:17:20,370 --> 00:17:21,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Resonance?</font>

175
00:17:21,870 --> 00:17:25,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've seen it on TV
and in the movies, haven't you?</font>

176
00:17:26,250 --> 00:17:28,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where people shatter glass
with just their voice?</font>

177
00:17:28,540 --> 00:17:29,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow!</font>

178
00:17:32,920 --> 00:17:34,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I'm not mistaken,
resonance occurs...</font>

179
00:17:34,880 --> 00:17:37,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...when the frequency of one's voice</font>

180
00:17:37,640 --> 00:17:41,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">matches the wavelength
of an object.</font>

181
00:17:42,430 --> 00:17:45,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But could such a phenomenon
be powerful enough</font>

182
00:17:45,480 --> 00:17:47,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to defeat a monster of that size?!</font>

183
00:17:53,150 --> 00:17:54,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That rooster...</font>

184
00:17:56,280 --> 00:17:57,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who is he?!</font>

185
00:19:02,010 --> 00:19:03,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no mark.</font>

186
00:19:03,640 --> 00:19:05,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It wasn't this one, after all.</font>

187
00:19:05,850 --> 00:19:07,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whew...</font>

188
00:19:07,890 --> 00:19:09,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is bad!</font>

189
00:19:10,520 --> 00:19:12,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your yard's destroyed, Old Man!</font>

190
00:19:18,240 --> 00:19:20,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you saying
you want to help clean?</font>

191
00:19:25,410 --> 00:19:27,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is anyone hurt?</font>

192
00:19:27,410 --> 00:19:29,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please be careful!</font>

193
00:19:32,250 --> 00:19:33,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Injured, coming through!</font>

194
00:19:35,380 --> 00:19:37,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are there anymore garbage bags?</font>

195
00:19:37,510 --> 00:19:39,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, we still have more.</font>

196
00:19:43,260 --> 00:19:44,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There we go!</font>

197
00:19:45,850 --> 00:19:48,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Phew, we're done!</font>

198
00:19:49,100 --> 00:19:52,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know, defeating Demons,
helping us clean...</font>

199
00:19:52,480 --> 00:19:54,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...you're one hell of a rooster!</font>

200
00:19:56,320 --> 00:19:57,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Where did he go?</font>

201
00:19:58,190 --> 00:19:59,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

202
00:20:02,450 --> 00:20:03,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Cluckers...</font>

203
00:20:04,580 --> 00:20:07,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}MAX CLEARANCE 2.4 METERS</font>

204
00:20:08,500 --> 00:20:10,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Cluckers...</font>

205
00:20:10,290 --> 00:20:11,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...is not my name.</font>

206
00:20:12,330 --> 00:20:13,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's Keiji.</font>

207
00:20:14,040 --> 00:20:15,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a born wanderer.</font>

208
00:20:16,380 --> 00:20:18,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's time I left this town.</font>

209
00:20:19,130 --> 00:20:22,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Old Man, I hope
I've paid you back for the feast.</font>

210
00:20:23,220 --> 00:20:24,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've defeated the Demon.</font>

211
00:20:25,720 --> 00:20:26,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And...</font>

212
00:20:27,810 --> 00:20:30,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I cleaned up the mess I made
in your yard.</font>

213
00:20:31,440 --> 00:20:33,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I leave no unfinished business
behind.</font>

214
00:20:34,480 --> 00:20:37,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's how I roll.</font>

215
00:20:41,030 --> 00:20:42,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now then...</font>

216
00:20:43,490 --> 00:20:44,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you leaving?!</font>

217
00:20:45,620 --> 00:20:49,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leaving a woman crying
isn't my style.</font>

218
00:20:50,040 --> 00:20:52,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry for the wait.
I'm back.</font>

219
00:21:07,220 --> 00:21:10,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The next town awaits me.</font>

220
00:22:50,990 --> 00:22:52,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, look!</font>

221
00:22:53,200 --> 00:22:56,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Check this out!</font>

222
00:22:57,920 --> 00:23:00,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Gross!
- Flasher!</font>

223
00:23:00,960 --> 00:23:04,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now that I have your attention...</font>

224
00:23:07,130 --> 00:23:08,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No one wants to see...</font>

225
00:23:08,630 --> 00:23:10,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">your dirty body!</font>

226
00:23:14,600 --> 00:23:15,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}THUNDERBIRD</font>

227
00:23:15,890 --> 00:23:18,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thunderbird!!</font>

228
00:23:27,150 --> 00:23:28,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Disgusting.</font>

